So, yeah. Moving down from Boss - Someone causes Luigi to land one tile to the left of This is Something. Pressing A, B, Y, or X on that spot causes you to enter the endless bonus game. And, the only direction you can move from that spot is left, which moves Luigi to Snow Furry Temple, where you can then move normally again.
